1. Videla sam *dugu* nakon kiše. (*dugu* - rainbow) (I saw a rainbow after the rain.)
2. U parku su zasadili *duge* cvetne aranžmane. (*duge* - long) (They planted long flower arrangements in the park.)
3. Moj prijatelj ima *duge* noge. (*duge* - long) (My friend has long legs.)
4. Nema kraja ovom *dugom* sastanku. (*dugom* - long) (This long meeting seems endless.)
5. Kada budem bila penzioner, planiram da putujem *duge* staze. (*duge* - long) (When I retire, I plan to travel long distances.)
6. U šumi sam videla *dugu* zmiju. (*dugu* - long) (I saw a long snake in the forest.)
7. *Duga* kosa ti savršeno pristaje. (*Duga* - long) (Long hair suits you perfectly.)
8. Deca su crtala *duge* po papiru. (*duge* - long) (The children drew long lines on the paper.) 
9. Njena haljina je bila prelepa, sa *dugim* šlepom. (*dugim* - long) (Her dress was beautiful, with a long train.)
10. U knjizi sam pročitala *dugu* i uzbudljivu priču. (*dugu* - long) (I read a long and exciting story in the book.)